                    <div class="media-body" id="joinUsInfo">
                        <h1>JOIN US</h1>
                        <p>HempBuyer Auction/Market (HBA) helps you with business development services by way of
                            introductions and transaction coordination. Our services are non exclusive. We win when you
                            win. Use HBA to augment and enhance your present sales & marketing efforts. </p>
                        <p> Stop wasting time sending out lab tests, pictures and samples to strangers over and over
                            again. Make your product postings one time and use our easy cut and paste links to market
                            your products to potential customers and your social media. </p>
                        <p> Minimize the tire kickers. You’ll be able to reach more potential customers and increase
                            sales of first-time customers who may be wary of transacting with a stranger. </p>
                        <p>Once a buyer has experienced a successful transaction with you through HBA member services,
                            the buyer will get to like your products, know and trust you. You can then move them into
                            buying more. Perhaps there is even a long term contract potential for your products and
                            services.
