                    <div class="media-body" id="sellingMadeEasier">
                        <h1>SELLING MADE EASIER - AUCTION/MARKET</h1>
                        <p>HBA offers multiple opportunities to help you sell your products, services and grow your
                            business. You only need to post your products once. Load your pictures, COAs and videos to
                            your product post. From your seller dashboard, easily copy and paste links of your products
                            to your potential customers. There is no more scrolling through your phone trying to find
                            that COA or video you KNOW you have SOMEWHERE! (How many times have we all done this?) Share
                            your links easily on your social media accounts.
                        </p>
                        <p><b>Auction Postings:</b> Offer your products as an auction. Sell to the highest bidder.
                            Buyers openly bid against one another for your product under your parameters. You can also
                            offer a “Buy Now” fixed price opportunity to buyers with this type of posting. MOQ (minimum
                            order quantity) may be offered with this type of listing. </p>

                        <p>The <b>Buy Now offer/with Auction </b>can be for the full amount of material offered or a MOQ
                            (minimum order quantity) of the quantity offered. </p>

                        <p>If a buyer purchases a portion of the quantity offered at the <b>Buy Now </b>price. Your
                            listing will automatically turn into a <b>Fixed Price/Buy Now</b> offering. If you choose,
                            you can relist your remaining product as an <b>Auction</b> again. <b>Auctions</b> can be
                            listed for <span class="hbaImp">8 days and be renewed automatically for up to 8
                                times.</span>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <b>Buy Now/Fixed Price Postings:</b> With a <b>Buy Now/Fixed Price</b> listing, a buyer
                            knows the price they need to pay for your item. You can fast track the transaction with your
                            coordinator and complete this transaction quickly.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            You work hard in your business. Let HBA handle some of the heavy lifting by helping you sell
                            your products and services. <b>Buy Now/Fixed Price</b> listings may be listed up to <span
                                class="hbaImp">30
                                days and be renewed automatically for up to 12 times.</span> This type of listing is
                            good
                            for regularly manufactured products.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <b>Make An Offer:</b> HBA created the <b>Make An Offer</b> featured listing for those
                            members who want to see what kind of offers may come in on a listing. The sellers are not
                            obligated to to accept any offer if it is under the suggested offer price listed by the
                            seller. This feature offers members an opportunity to haggle. An offer is a binding
                            agreement between the buyer and seller. Cancelling an offer is possible, under certain
                            circumstances. If the item’s description is significantly different from the item, if you
                            entered the wrong amount or if the seller is not responding to your offer. Contact customer
                            service if you have any questions. <a
                                href="mailto:support@hempbuyer.com">support@hempbuyer.com. </a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
