                    <div class="media-body" id="payment">
                        <h1>PAYMENT</h1>
                        <h3>LIFECYCLE OF TRANSACTIONS < $2500.00</h3>
                                <p>For transactions $2500.00 or less, buyers make their purchase → Seller is
                                    notified→Buyer populates his shipping address → Seller populates shipping cost → HBA
                                    System generates invoice → Buyer makes purchase with ACH through Buyer dashboard →
                                    Seller provides tracking number to buyer via dashboard → Ships product → Seller is
                                    paid → Success, transaction complete.</p>

